<h1 id="page-header" class="page-header">Page header</h1>

<p>A simple shell for an <code>h1</code> to appropriately space out and segment sections of content on a
    page. It can utilize the <code>h1</code>'s default <code>small</code> element, as well as most other
    components (with additional styles).</p>

<div class="bs-example">
    <div class="page-header">
        <h1>Example page header
            <small>Subtext for header</small>
        </h1>
    </div>
</div>
